Package com.ngrok.services

Class SshCertificateAuthorities

java.lang.Object
com.ngrok.services.SshCertificateAuthorities
public class SshCertificateAuthorities extends Object
An SSH Certificate Authority is a pair of an SSH Certificate and its private key that can be used to sign other SSH host and user certificates. See also https://ngrok.com/docs/api#api-ssh-certificate-authorities.
